  "prompt": "What is the best website to buy customized T-shirts in India?",
  "response": "There are several websites in India that offer high-quality customized T-shirts. Here are some popular and reliable options:\n\n1. **Bewakoof**  \n   - Known for trendy designs and affordable pricing.\n   - Offers customization options with unique prints and slogans.\n   - Website: [bewakoof.com](https://www.bewakoof.com)\n\n2. **Vistaprint India**  \n   - Specializes in customized products, including T-shirts.\n   - Allows you to upload your own designs or choose from templates.\n   - Website: [vistaprint.in](https://www.vistaprint.in)\n\n3. **PrintVenue**  \n   - Offers a wide range of customization options for T-shirts.\n   - Good quality fabrics and printing techniques.\n   - Website: [printvenue.com](https://www.printvenue.com)\n\n4. **Zoho**  \n   - Known for high-quality custom apparel.\n   - Offers a variety of styles and fabrics for T-shirts.\n   - Website: [zoho.com](https://www.zoho.com)\n\n5. **The Souled Store**  \n   - Focuses on pop culture and quirky designs.\n   - Allows customization with unique artwork and slogans.\n   - Website: [thesouledstore.com](https://www.thesouledstore.com)\n\n6. **Meesho**  \n   - Affordable and customizable T-shirts for personal or business use.\n   - Popular for bulk orders.\n   - Website: [meesho.com](https://www.meesho.com)\n\n7. **Customloot**  \n   - Specializes in custom-designed T-shirts and apparel.\n   - Offers a user-friendly design tool.\n   - Website: [customloot.com](https://www.customloot.com)\n\nWhen choosing a website, consider factors like pricing, fabric quality, printing techniques, and delivery time. Many of these platforms provide customer reviews and ratings, which can help you make an informed decision.",
  "temperature": 1.0,
